Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you won't be able to save \Nthe two in the basement!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.34,0:00:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yu, Ayumi. It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.76,0:00:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.56,0:00:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.31,0:00:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's our big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.52,0:00:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There was a reason behind it,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.02,0:00:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I had someone delete\Nyour memories pertaining to me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.90,0:00:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.78,0:00:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.. There was a lot going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.20,0:00:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like it, Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.66,0:00:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yu, you finally were fully aware of using\Nan ability you took via your "plunder".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.92,0:00:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I had you come\Nhere with Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.38,0:00:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In either case, I would have ended\Nup here... that's convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.47,0:00:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.30,0:00:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.81,0:01:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you used my time-leap...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.39,0:01:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...that was a job well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.23,0:01:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's going to happen now?\NCan I go back together with you, Big Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.11,0:01:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,More like the reverse. You can\Nplunder any ability you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.15,0:01:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You are the strongest \Nof all ability wielders.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.11,0:01:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And, you even have the \Npower of time-leap now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.32,0:01:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that is too much of a menace
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.53,0:01:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.12,0:01:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are syndicates abound\Nthat would try to use your powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.08,0:01:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you live life as\Nyou have been until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have to spend your days here\Nuntil those abilities dissipate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.59,0:01:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.50,0:01:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You may already know,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.88,0:01:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but this is a research facility\Nfor the special abilities we created.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.93,0:01:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,\Nthis is the safest place in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.81,0:01:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.02,0:01:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 11: Charlotte
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.99,0:02:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My, my, nice of you to come by.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.37,0:02:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That old man is the leader of the\Nresearch team, Dr. Tsutsumiuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.50,0:02:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.08,0:02:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...he's the one that saved me back then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.13,0:02:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And this is..?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.17,0:02:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is a research facility that \Nis creating a vaccine to prevent
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.79,0:02:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,future outbreaks of special abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.64,0:02:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vaccine? Are we all ill?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.60,0:02:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The special abilities are truly a disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.39,0:02:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, before particles are spread\Nall over Earth again,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.94,0:02:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we need to vaccinate\Nevery person in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.07,0:02:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Particles?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.44,0:02:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever heard of a\Nlong-orbit comet named Charlotte?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.86,0:02:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ayu knows about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you must really like the stars a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.37,0:02:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Star-gazing is my hobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.54,0:02:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The comet Charlotte approaches\NEarth in 75-year cycles.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.42,0:02:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And when it does, an unknown\Nparticle is showered onto Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:02:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those who inhale the particles
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.13,0:03:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,generate special powers
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.26,0:03:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,when they are most sensitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The particles that snuck all the \Nway into the cerebral nerves
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.27,0:03:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,dig up and awaken a sector that\Nis supposed to stay dormant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.60,0:03:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And that is the reason behind these powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.82,0:03:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For instance,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.86,0:03:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,roughly 400 years ago we had an\Nextremely close encounter,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.57,0:03:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and many particles showered down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.82,0:03:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In Europe, some of those that inhaled the\Nparticles became witches with special powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.74,0:03:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And, the people who feared the\Nabilities conducted a witch hunt,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.71,0:03:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and tens of thousands of ability\Nwielders were slaughtered.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That comet grazed the atmosphere\Nagain roughly 12 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.84,0:03:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and young folk started to wield\Nspecial powers one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.39,0:03:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yu, he's talking about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.89,0:03:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that doesn't happen\Nagain in the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.27,0:03:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we are making a vaccine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.19,0:03:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Production has already begun in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we can rest assured now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.48,0:03:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, only Japan that I\Ncontrol is under protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.49,0:04:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Witch hunts are still happening\Nall over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, that has nothing to do with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.66,0:04:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This story can't possibly be that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.12,0:04:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The ability-wielders overseas have banded up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're in a situation where we don't know\Nwhen they will cause terror in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about the vaccine?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can curb the number of infected that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.47,0:04:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but it doesn't do anything for the\Npeople who already developed their abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.72,0:04:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, all you have to do is\Nmake a wonder drug to counter it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.51,0:04:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Otosaka... you are indeed a sharp one,\Nbut I guess your little brother isn't so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It takes a very long time \Nto create a new drug.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know what's going to happen next,\Nbut I will make sure to protect you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right... but at least I'd like Ayumi to\Nregain her memories about you, Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.37,0:04:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why? I was able to regain my memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know why you were\Nthe only one that regained memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.50,0:05:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was there a large factor somewhere that\Ncaused it, or was it just coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.13,0:05:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In either case, as we stand now,\Nthat's an impossibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be...\NThat's too sad for Ayumi....
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From today, we can make new\Nmemories as siblings again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.52,0:05:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.10,0:05:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your oldest brother, Shunsuke.\NI'm blind, but it's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.61,0:05:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, can I call you Big Brother Shun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She accepted that real quick!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to see your\Nschool friends for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but these guys are your friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.21,0:05:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,as well as ability wielders.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.04,0:05:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Ayumi Otosaka! Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.63,0:05:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you. Shichino,\Nwhy don't you walk through a wall for starters?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.30,0:05:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing... don't petrify yourself\Nfrom fear by seeing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.97,0:05:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.81,0:05:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The recreation room here is pretty substantial.\NThere's lots of fun things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.77,0:06:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about music? Can I listen to Haro-haro?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.53,0:06:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.49,0:06:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be teaching you academics.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.33,0:06:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like everyone is keeping\Ntheir distance from just ne...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.58,0:06:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait? Is everyone gone already?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.55,0:06:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They call the first one the Bunei Invasion,\Nand the second one the Koan Invasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a sister complex?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not... really...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're fretting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.85,0:06:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your big brother took Ayu away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, can you come\Nhang out with me a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to play for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Play?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:07:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right... got a good hand.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Reach!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ron.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Double value tiles, little three dragons,\Nhalf-flush, all triplets, three dora tiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.34,0:07:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sanbaiman as dealer, so 36000 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.63,0:07:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing. This is the first time I've seen\Nsomeone lose all points in the first hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really suck at this.\NAre you really Shunsuke's little brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit... let me play one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.73,0:07:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.19,0:07:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Found one, so I'm leaving the table...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.11,0:07:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As always, it's rather sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since I can't choose to go\Nlook for them it's all too random...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It would be so much easier if I could\Nknow who wields an ability when...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just find?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about an ability \Nwielder, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.67,0:07:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So he didn't have to be \Ndrenched in water for that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.38,0:07:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Which means, you're headed \Nto the student council?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can I come along with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.38,0:07:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.97,0:07:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're the ability wielder that is the least\Nable to step outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you lack self-awareness?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see... that's how it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:07:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tomori... I wonder how she's doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, why am I thinking about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.03,0:08:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please head over to Hoshinoumi Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.32,0:08:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Furuki, is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No... it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you turn the corner?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Furuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.47,0:08:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Kumagami!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have to take you to a different location!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.52,0:08:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My family...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.31,0:08:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're threatening my family...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.81,0:08:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you had family?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If they found out I had one,\NI have to quit the syndicate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is the rule, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.90,0:08:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I prided myself in being able to help you\Nguys as an alum... forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,0:09:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh... looks like this is going\Nto be a bit troublesome....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:12.17,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ishihara Mountain Industry
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.38,0:09:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Over here. Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.64,0:09:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I brought him here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.01,0:09:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.06,0:09:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, mighty one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.82,0:09:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Welcome, mighty one."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A foreigner? Oh, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is enough, right? \NGive me back my family!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet. There is one more \Nthing we need you to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.91,0:09:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll contact you later. Now leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.95,0:09:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what you said before!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.83,0:09:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You do want to meet your family, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"You do want to meet your family, right?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. Furuki, you can\Njust think about your family...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.59,0:09:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure he does not die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where... is this...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My head feels woozy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Looks like they injected\Na truth serum or something...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.09,0:10:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to make me tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Information about every psychic you are\Naware of that you are hiding from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.39,0:10:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'd tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.77,0:10:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My teeth are gonna be all gone...\NI'm gonna have dentures at this age?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.30,0:11:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I told them anything and \Neverything, didn't I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.14,0:11:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Shunsuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.30,0:12:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You are the one who gathered all\Nthe psychics in this country, yes?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.35,0:12:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This guy isn't Japanese..?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If so, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.19,0:12:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had Kumagami tell me who the\Nstrongest psychic in this country was.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kumagami did? That means he's\Nthe victim of an overseas terrorist...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about Kumagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.95,0:12:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His life is not in danger. However,\Nhe has no nails nor teeth now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the hell...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.54,0:12:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.37,0:12:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We would like to have Yu Otosaka.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.54,0:12:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That'll never happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We have kidnapped a psychic\Nby the name of Nao Tomori.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We would like him in return\Nfor both Tomori and Kumagami.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where at?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.72,0:12:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Furuki will take you there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Furuki will?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.72,0:12:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I would like Yu Otosaka to come by himself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.10,0:12:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have heard about you all\Nfrom Furuki and Kumagami.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.93,0:12:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This operation has been planned\Nfrom quite a while back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.60,0:12:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If the plans diverge,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:12:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}we will assume you traveled\Nto the past to change destinies,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.73,0:13:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and kill off Furuki's family. See you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That far...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.83,0:13:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Phone call, Furuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's you, Otosaka...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Furuki... are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They threatened me... I'm sorry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.59,0:13:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How long have they been threatening you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.93,0:13:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Back around when we were\Ngetting ready to build the academy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.35,0:13:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This makes it pretty tough...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.47,0:13:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I talked, they said \Nthey would kill my family.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought about suicide... but I couldn't\Nleave my family behind... so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.36,0:13:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why all of this happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.32,0:13:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's an error in my judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is no need for\Nyou to torment yourself, Furuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will make sure to rescue your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.37,0:13:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm really sorry...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.16,0:13:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So they've made it out to Japan as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, how did they get Kumagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.96,0:13:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They are threatening Furuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.88,0:14:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was my mistake. He had a family,\Nbut I gave tacit consent...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To think the enemy would\Ncome in from that angle...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.05,0:14:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what if you had your little \Nbrother time-leap to before
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furuki started getting threatened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.22,0:14:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If he was threatened from before \Nthe academy was built...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure if we can follow \Nthe same path or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.48,0:14:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Which means, there is a possibility that\Nthis entire syndicate may not even exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.11,0:14:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The risk is just too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.24,0:14:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, how about we have your\Nlittle brother rescue Kumagami first?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we do that, Furuki's family will be sacrificed...\Nthey can notice such anomalies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.58,0:14:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, how about using an ability\Nwielder other than your little brother—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.21,0:14:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They told me Yu needs to go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.79,0:14:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we screw up, everyone caught by them\Nwill fall victim to their hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing we can do, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds more like we have a better shot\Nif we let the little brother go in by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.47,0:14:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're probably against ability wielders,\Nso he can plunder their abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.43,0:14:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he screws up, he can use time-leap\Nto redo everything from this point in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.27,0:15:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That way, there won't be any irregularities,\Nso they won't notice that he time-leaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have to bet on Yu now, don't we...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So unbecoming... what a sight...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.88,0:15:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tomori is held hostage?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.92,0:15:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Many security guards at \Nthe dorm were put down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.55,0:15:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is no doubt these are\Npros that came from overseas....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm sure they're armed as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to go to a place\Nlike that... by myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.01,0:15:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it. It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.39,0:15:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,First off, plunder all the abilities \Nof everyone in the area,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and make them drop their weapons. \NYou can do that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.19,0:15:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it's not a hidden enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.23,0:15:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy wants you. They\Nwon't do anything that would kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, if you get caught, or they put\NNao or Kumagami in harm's way,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.49,0:15:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,use your time-leap ability to\Ncome back to this point in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:15:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can build a new tactic at that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.46,0:16:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One more thing, make sure \Nto never get too excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.50,0:16:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your collapse power will trigger,\Nand your own life will be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.55,0:16:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Got that, Yu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.17,0:16:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.13,0:16:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's with all this! There's\Nno way I can do something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a problem that one\Nindividual can handle on his own!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.06,0:16:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was just someone that got \Ngood grades by unfair means,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.31,0:16:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nothing more than a fiend of cheating!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.98,0:16:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a despicable guy that\Nhas only thought about himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am just a greedy human that wanted\Neveryone to see me in a good light!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I am... what can I--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.62,0:16:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.54,0:16:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to my heartbeat.\NConcentrate on only that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.96,0:16:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you calm now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.38,0:16:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... I was rushing things too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.05,0:16:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you feel you're in trouble, time-leap \Nback to this point in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:16:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all you need to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We still have a bit of time left.\NCalmly think it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.61,0:17:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However... you seem like you'd be\Npopular from just your looks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.74,0:17:13.18,Italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was there also a need to play the role of \Na genius by cheating as much as possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.18,0:17:14.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the real question.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It really was a horrible start for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.58,0:17:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To do some investigation, of course.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But my dream is to film a ZHIEND music video.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That is why I decided that I'll stick it out with you,\Nuntil you have risen back up to normal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.75,0:17:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was the same thing with Ayumi...\Nit's too late to realize something after losing it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will make sure to rescue Tomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've accepted your fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.73,0:17:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll follow you in a bit. You are not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.27,0:17:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If something happens, we'll \Nrescue you right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So are you Furuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.32,0:17:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.20,0:17:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.07,0:18:02.00,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ishihara Mountain Industry
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I brought him here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}People in the field of vision...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just these two.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.63,0:18:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But they're adults... and \Nnot ability wielders.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.51,0:18:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, as promised, I will\Nrelease your family to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.51,0:18:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the key to the condo.\NThe location is written on the tag.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.52,0:18:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... this was the \Nonly thing I could do...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.57,0:18:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's do this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're not armed..?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.96,0:18:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you satisfied now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.13,0:18:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Tomori?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.13,0:18:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right below us... both of \Nthem are in the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.64,0:19:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Release both of them right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not good... I must time-leap...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.49,0:19:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We made you unable to use\Npsychic powers to travel to the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So it is indeed impossible with one eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.00,0:19:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you use your psychic powers of collapse,\Nyou won't be able to save the two in the basement!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:19:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Hurry, hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:19:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Shit! That wasn't necessary!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good! There is a\Ncollapse happening right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's not using his time-leap?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.08,0:20:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks it... what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.05,0:20:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.10,0:20:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is this time to be just standing around?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.51,0:20:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have to go save them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.97,0:20:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.77,0:20:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How does it look?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.90,0:20:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It looks hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.73,0:20:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But we still have to search for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.44,0:20:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nao!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.03,0:20:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kumagami! Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.16,0:20:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shunsuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.78,0:20:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are those the main culprits?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.83,0:20:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Medoki, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.29,0:20:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.37,0:20:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Found the little brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.29,0:20:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He blocked it in the nick \Nof time with telekinesis...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.84,0:20:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. He's still alive. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.59,0:21:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They ruined one eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why he couldn't leap...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.80,0:21:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please take him to somewhere safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.81,0:21:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.72,0:21:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that you alone were all right
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because of your ability, but the \Nother two are already dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.36,0:21:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you... Kumagami... Nao...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.19,0:21:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Found them! Both of them are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.83,0:21:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kumagami!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.16,0:21:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kumagami, where are you?\NAnswer me, Kumagami!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kuma—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.92,0:21:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kumagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you... Shunsuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.14,0:21:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is enough... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.98,0:21:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kumagami! You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.69,0:21:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't allow it! You have to\Ncontinue to be at my side!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.86,0:22:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is asking for the impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.40,0:22:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can't! I won't allow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.82,0:22:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kumagami, don't go off on \Nyour own! Don't go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.08,0:22:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shunsuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.12,0:22:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, the nickname "Pooh"...\Nwas a lie after all...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.88,0:22:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kumagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.63,0:22:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kumagami...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.47,0:22:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KUMAGAMI!
